name: genesis: brooklyn bridge dusk 2
description:
Pic 3 of 3.
In 2000 I visited New York and brought 1 Roll of film and a cheap point & shoot. The film was underexposed, had light leaks and all kinds of errors. But 3 frames made all the difference: It was the start of my love for photography! 
I hope to inspire you to fall in love with the magic that photography reveals in your mind.
